                <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;flowchart TD\n    A[\&quot;🏗️ System Design Patterns\\nBuilding Blocks of Large Systems\&quot;] --&gt; B[\&quot;📋 CRUD Systems\&quot;]\n    A --&gt; C[\&quot;🎫 Booking Systems\&quot;]\n    A --&gt; D[\&quot;⚡ Real-Time Systems\&quot;]\n    A --&gt; E[\&quot;📱 Feed Systems\&quot;]\n    A --&gt; F[\&quot;📍 Tracking Systems\&quot;]\n    A --&gt; G[\&quot;🎬 Streaming Systems\&quot;]\n    A --&gt; H[\&quot;📊 Analytics Systems\&quot;]\n\n    B[\&quot;📋 CRUD Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• Employee Management\\n• Inventory Management\\n• Hospital Records\\n• Hotel Management\\n\\n⚙️ Core Operations:\\n• Create (POST)\\n• Read (GET)\\n• Update (PUT/PATCH)\\n• Delete (DELETE)\\n\\n🔍 Main Discussion:\\n• Database Design (Schema, Normalization)\\n• Search (Indexing, Full-Text)\\n• Access Control (RBAC, Permissions)\\n\\n🏛️ Architecture:\\nClient → API Gateway → Service Layer → Database\&quot;]\n\n    C[\&quot;🎫 Booking Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• BookMyShow\\n• Flight Booking\\n• Hotel Booking\\n• Train Reservation\\n\\n⚠️ Core Challenge:\\n• Concurrency &amp; Race Conditions\\n• &#39;Last seat available - Two users click simultaneously - Who gets it?&#39;\\n\\n🔒 Main Discussion:\\n• Locking (Pessimistic vs Optimistic)\\n• Consistency (ACID vs BASE)\\n• Transactions (Isolation Levels)\\n• Idempotency\\n• Queue-based Booking\&quot;]\n\n    D[\&quot;⚡ Real-Time Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• Ludo / Chess (Multiplayer Games)\\n• WhatsApp (Chat)\\n• Collaborative Whiteboard\\n• Live Sports Scores\\n\\n⚠️ Core Challenge:\\n• State Synchronization\\n• Keeping all clients in sync in real-time\\n\\n🔌 Main Discussion:\\n• WebSocket (Persistent Connections)\\n• Pub/Sub (Message Broadcasting)\\n• Event Ordering (Sequence Numbers)\\n• Reconnection &amp; State Recovery\\n• Conflict Resolution (OT/CRDT)\&quot;]\n\n    E[\&quot;📱 Feed Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• Facebook Feed\\n• Instagram Feed\\n• LinkedIn Feed\\n• Twitter Timeline\\n\\n⚠️ Core Challenge:\\n• Ranking (Relevance Algorithm)\\n• Aggregation (Content Mix)\\n• Massive Reads (Millions of users)\\n\\n📦 Main Discussion:\\n• Fanout (Push vs Pull vs Hybrid)\\n• Caching (Redis, CDN)\\n• Feed Generation (Pre-computation)\\n• Personalization (ML Ranking)\\n• Pagination (Cursor-based)\&quot;]\n\n    F[\&quot;📍 Tracking Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• Uber / Lyft\\n• Food Delivery (Zomato, DoorDash)\\n• Fleet Tracking\\n• Package Delivery\\n\\n⚠️ Core Challenge:\\n• Location Updates\\n• Tracking millions of moving objects\\n\\n🗺️ Main Discussion:\\n• Geospatial Indexing (GeoHash, S2, Quadtree)\\n• Nearby Search (Radius Queries)\\n• Real-time Updates (Streaming)\\n• ETA Calculation\\n• Driver-Rider Matching\&quot;]\n\n    G[\&quot;🎬 Streaming Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• YouTube\\n• Netflix\\n• Spotify\\n• Twitch\\n\\n⚠️ Core Challenge:\\n• Large Content Delivery\\n• Streaming high-bandwidth content\\n\\n🌐 Main Discussion:\\n• CDN (Content Delivery Network)\\n• Chunking (Adaptive Bitrate)\\n• Storage (Object Storage - S3)\\n• Pre-fetching &amp; Buffering\\n• DRM &amp; Content Protection\&quot;]\n\n    H[\&quot;📊 Analytics Systems\\n\\n📌 Examples:\\n• Metrics Platform\\n• Event Tracking (Google Analytics)\\n• Monitoring (Prometheus)\\n• Log Aggregation\\n\\n⚠️ Core Challenge:\\n• Huge Write Volume\\n• Millions of events per second\\n\\n📈 Main Discussion:\\n• Kafka (Event Streaming)\\n• Batch Processing (Spark, Flink)\\n• Aggregation (Time-series DB)\\n• Data Retention Policies\\n• Real-time Dashboards\&quot;]\n\n    style A fill:#1a1a2e,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:4px,font-size:16px\n    style B fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px\n    style C fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px\n    style D fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px\n    style E fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px\n    style F fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px\n    style G fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px\n    style H fill:#0f3460,color:#ffffff,stroke:#e94560,stroke-width:2px&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="2">
