                <UserObject label="&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;📋 CRUD Systems&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;📌 Examples:&lt;br&gt;• Employee Management&lt;br&gt;• Inventory Management&lt;br&gt;• Hospital Records&lt;br&gt;• Hotel Management&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;⚙️ Core Operations:&lt;br&gt;• Create (POST)&lt;br&gt;• Read (GET)&lt;br&gt;• Update (PUT/PATCH)&lt;br&gt;• Delete (DELETE)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔍 Main Discussion:&lt;br&gt;• Database Design (Schema, Normalization)&lt;br&gt;• Search (Indexing, Full-Text)&lt;br&gt;• Access Control (RBAC, Permissions)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🏛️ Architecture:&lt;br&gt;Client → API Gateway → Service Layer → Database&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:B" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="📋 CRUD Systems&#xa;&#xa;📌 Examples:&#xa;• Employee Management&#xa;• Inventory Management&#xa;• Hospital Records&#xa;• Hotel Management&#xa;&#xa;⚙️ Core Operations:&#xa;• Create (POST)&#xa;• Read (GET)&#xa;• Update (PUT/PATCH)&#xa;• Delete (DELETE)&#xa;&#xa;🔍 Main Discussion:&#xa;• Database Design (Schema, Normalization)&#xa;• Search (Indexing, Full-Text)&#xa;• Access Control (RBAC, Permissions)&#xa;&#xa;🏛️ Architecture:&#xa;Client → API Gateway → Service Layer → Database" id="12">
