                <UserObject label="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;🎫 Booking Systems&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;📌 Examples:&lt;br&gt;• BookMyShow&lt;br&gt;• Flight Booking&lt;br&gt;• Hotel Booking&lt;br&gt;• Train Reservation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⚠️ Core Challenge:&lt;br&gt;• Concurrency &amp;amp; Race Conditions&lt;br&gt;• &#39;Last seat available - Two users click simultaneously - Who gets it?&#39;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔒 Main Discussion:&lt;br&gt;• Locking (Pessimistic vs Optimistic)&lt;br&gt;• Consistency (ACID vs BASE)&lt;br&gt;• Transactions (Isolation Levels)&lt;br&gt;• Idempotency&lt;br&gt;• Queue-based Booking&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:C" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="🎫 Booking Systems&#xa;&#xa;📌 Examples:&#xa;• BookMyShow&#xa;• Flight Booking&#xa;• Hotel Booking&#xa;• Train Reservation&#xa;&#xa;⚠️ Core Challenge:&#xa;• Concurrency &amp; Race Conditions&#xa;• &#39;Last seat available - Two users click simultaneously - Who gets it?&#39;&#xa;&#xa;🔒 Main Discussion:&#xa;• Locking (Pessimistic vs Optimistic)&#xa;• Consistency (ACID vs BASE)&#xa;• Transactions (Isolation Levels)&#xa;• Idempotency&#xa;• Queue-based Booking" id="13">
