                <UserObject label="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;⚡ Real-Time Systems&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;📌 Examples:&lt;br&gt;• Ludo / Chess (Multiplayer Games)&lt;br&gt;• WhatsApp (Chat)&lt;br&gt;• Collaborative Whiteboard&lt;br&gt;• Live Sports Scores&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⚠️ Core Challenge:&lt;br&gt;• State Synchronization&lt;br&gt;• Keeping all clients in sync in real-time&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔌 Main Discussion:&lt;br&gt;• WebSocket (Persistent Connections)&lt;br&gt;• Pub/Sub (Message Broadcasting)&lt;br&gt;• Event Ordering (Sequence Numbers)&lt;br&gt;• Reconnection &amp;amp; State Recovery&lt;br&gt;• Conflict Resolution (OT/CRDT)&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:D" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="⚡ Real-Time Systems&#xa;&#xa;📌 Examples:&#xa;• Ludo / Chess (Multiplayer Games)&#xa;• WhatsApp (Chat)&#xa;• Collaborative Whiteboard&#xa;• Live Sports Scores&#xa;&#xa;⚠️ Core Challenge:&#xa;• State Synchronization&#xa;• Keeping all clients in sync in real-time&#xa;&#xa;🔌 Main Discussion:&#xa;• WebSocket (Persistent Connections)&#xa;• Pub/Sub (Message Broadcasting)&#xa;• Event Ordering (Sequence Numbers)&#xa;• Reconnection &amp; State Recovery&#xa;• Conflict Resolution (OT/CRDT)" id="14">
