                <UserObject label="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;📍 Tracking Systems&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;📌 Examples:&lt;br&gt;• Uber / Lyft&lt;br&gt;• Food Delivery (Zomato, DoorDash)&lt;br&gt;• Fleet Tracking&lt;br&gt;• Package Delivery&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⚠️ Core Challenge:&lt;br&gt;• Location Updates&lt;br&gt;• Tracking millions of moving objects&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🗺️ Main Discussion:&lt;br&gt;• Geospatial Indexing (GeoHash, S2, Quadtree)&lt;br&gt;• Nearby Search (Radius Queries)&lt;br&gt;• Real-time Updates (Streaming)&lt;br&gt;• ETA Calculation&lt;br&gt;• Driver-Rider Matching&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:F" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="📍 Tracking Systems&#xa;&#xa;📌 Examples:&#xa;• Uber / Lyft&#xa;• Food Delivery (Zomato, DoorDash)&#xa;• Fleet Tracking&#xa;• Package Delivery&#xa;&#xa;⚠️ Core Challenge:&#xa;• Location Updates&#xa;• Tracking millions of moving objects&#xa;&#xa;🗺️ Main Discussion:&#xa;• Geospatial Indexing (GeoHash, S2, Quadtree)&#xa;• Nearby Search (Radius Queries)&#xa;• Real-time Updates (Streaming)&#xa;• ETA Calculation&#xa;• Driver-Rider Matching" id="16">
