                <UserObject label="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;🎬 Streaming Systems&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;📌 Examples:&lt;br&gt;• YouTube&lt;br&gt;• Netflix&lt;br&gt;• Spotify&lt;br&gt;• Twitch&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⚠️ Core Challenge:&lt;br&gt;• Large Content Delivery&lt;br&gt;• Streaming high-bandwidth content&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🌐 Main Discussion:&lt;br&gt;• CDN (Content Delivery Network)&lt;br&gt;• Chunking (Adaptive Bitrate)&lt;br&gt;• Storage (Object Storage - S3)&lt;br&gt;• Pre-fetching &amp;amp; Buffering&lt;br&gt;• DRM &amp;amp; Content Protection&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:G" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="🎬 Streaming Systems&#xa;&#xa;📌 Examples:&#xa;• YouTube&#xa;• Netflix&#xa;• Spotify&#xa;• Twitch&#xa;&#xa;⚠️ Core Challenge:&#xa;• Large Content Delivery&#xa;• Streaming high-bandwidth content&#xa;&#xa;🌐 Main Discussion:&#xa;• CDN (Content Delivery Network)&#xa;• Chunking (Adaptive Bitrate)&#xa;• Storage (Object Storage - S3)&#xa;• Pre-fetching &amp; Buffering&#xa;• DRM &amp; Content Protection" id="17">
