                <UserObject label="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;📊 Analytics Systems&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;📌 Examples:&lt;br&gt;• Metrics Platform&lt;br&gt;• Event Tracking (Google Analytics)&lt;br&gt;• Monitoring (Prometheus)&lt;br&gt;• Log Aggregation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⚠️ Core Challenge:&lt;br&gt;• Huge Write Volume&lt;br&gt;• Millions of events per second&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;📈 Main Discussion:&lt;br&gt;• Kafka (Event Streaming)&lt;br&gt;• Batch Processing (Spark, Flink)&lt;br&gt;• Aggregation (Time-series DB)&lt;br&gt;• Data Retention Policies&lt;br&gt;• Real-time Dashboards&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:H" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="📊 Analytics Systems&#xa;&#xa;📌 Examples:&#xa;• Metrics Platform&#xa;• Event Tracking (Google Analytics)&#xa;• Monitoring (Prometheus)&#xa;• Log Aggregation&#xa;&#xa;⚠️ Core Challenge:&#xa;• Huge Write Volume&#xa;• Millions of events per second&#xa;&#xa;📈 Main Discussion:&#xa;• Kafka (Event Streaming)&#xa;• Batch Processing (Spark, Flink)&#xa;• Aggregation (Time-series DB)&#xa;• Data Retention Policies&#xa;• Real-time Dashboards" id="18">
